Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\bord0.1\blur15\be7\3c&000000\3a&66}作品中讲述的故事
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)}{\bord0.1\blur15\be7\3c&000000\3a&66}终究与现实不同
