Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.27,0:01:29.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)}{\bord0.1\blur15\be7\3c&000000\3a&66}岁月蹉跎后仍是外人
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.82,0:02:53.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}老爸决定再婚了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.74,0:02:58.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}对方在上司带我去过的店里工作
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.45,0:03:01.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}还照顾过喝得烂醉的我
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.66,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你该不会被骗了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}放心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}亚季子绝对不是那种人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.46,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你今晚见到她就明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}今晚?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.76,0:03:14.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}好烫
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}大家见个面
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.39,0:03:18.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}时间定在你打工结束后
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}又搞突然袭击
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.19,0:03:31.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\3c&4C4C4C\4c&4C4C4C}真的准备好了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\bord2}{\3c&4C4C4C\4c&4C4C4C}好烫好烫
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}你说什么?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}好烫
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}只要老爸过得幸福就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我还是和以前一样
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}不能和以前一样了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}你有妹妹了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}妹妹?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}没错，妹妹
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}亚季子的女儿
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}初次见面
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.35,0:04:08.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我是绫濑亚季子
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.27,0:04:11.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}不好意思，把忙着打工的你叫了出来
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}没关系
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我是他儿子，浅村悠太
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&312E4C\4c&312E4C}{\bord2.5}你也来打声招呼
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.08,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&312E4C\4c&312E4C}{\bord2.5}初次见面
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&312E4C\4c&312E4C}{\bord2.5}我是绫濑沙季
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}老爸
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.88,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}沙季和你一样大
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.42,0:04:34.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}今年17岁，读高二
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.59,0:04:39.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}不过你的生日比她早一周
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}抱歉让你误会了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}沙季这孩子长大后，就完全不让我拍照了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}沙季这孩子长大后，就完全不让我拍照了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.47,0:04:50.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}我的眼神看着有些凶，不上镜
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&274766\4c&274766}不过我终于放心了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}毕竟是要一起生活的人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我之前还担心对方会不会很可怕
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.37,0:05:06.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}这可不好说
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}真正可怕的人也会摆出和颜悦色的模样
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&202B34\4c&202B34}听说你每天都在打工
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.67,0:05:15.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&202B34\4c&202B34}为上大学积攒学费
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.17,0:05:17.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&202B34\4c&202B34}成绩也非常优秀
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&202B34\4c&202B34}高智商罪犯也不在少数
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}对了，趁妈妈他们还没出来
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.31,0:05:34.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}我有些话想跟你说
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}不能对父母说吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.69,0:05:36.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}是的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.57,0:05:39.94,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}干脆挑明，那些话只能跟你说
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.49,0:05:44.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}这点时间就得到你的信任了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}我真厉害啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}你的幽默
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&475C66\4c&475C66}{\bord2.5}谈吐
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.83,0:05:54.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&475C66\4c&475C66}{\bord2.5}还有表情
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.46,0:05:58.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}都让人感受不到热情
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}所以
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.13,0:06:05.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}或许你能理解我的话
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我对你不抱有任何期待
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.32,0:06:24.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}也希望你不要对我抱有期待
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.70,0:06:30.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}你应该能理解，我在说什么吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}我放心了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}终于放心了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}从这一刻起
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}嗯，我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}从这一刻起
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我们以后就这样相处吧，绫濑
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}谢谢你，浅村
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.83,0:07:12.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}悠太
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你知道除臭剂放在哪里吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}电视机旁边
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你昨天给窗帘用过，之后一直放在那
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.92,0:07:22.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}是这样吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}谢了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.18,0:07:28.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}都这会儿了还慌什么
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}我本来想晚点收拾卧室
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}可一开始打扫就变得耿耿于怀
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.56,0:07:36.60,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&666666\4c&666666}要是被吐槽气味不好就难受了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&666666\4c&666666}太矫情了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&666666\4c&666666}到了我这个年纪
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}被吐槽会要人命的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.78,0:07:44.61,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}悠太
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.37,0:07:50.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&473B66\4c&473B66}{\bord3}一想到今后要打扰你们了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&242B4C\4c&242B4C}一想到今后要打扰你们了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&242B4C\4c&242B4C}就忍不住买了些礼物
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}别在意
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&242B4C\4c&242B4C}我妈妈不会拒绝别人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.84,0:08:04.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&242B4C\4c&242B4C}人家推荐啥，她就买啥
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&473B66\4c&473B66}我说沙季
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.97,0:08:08.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&473B66\4c&473B66}我在你口中好像成了没用的大人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&473B66\4c&473B66}可这是事实
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}是柑橘的香味
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}家里居然这么整洁
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.48,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}因为这几天一直忙着打扫
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.48,0:08:22.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}果然如太一先生所说
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.07,0:08:24.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}你们很爱干净呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.86,0:08:26.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}要保证精神的健康
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.95,0:08:29.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}就要先保证居所的整洁
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}居所要一尘不染
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.45,0:08:34.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}是浅村家的家训
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.54,0:08:36.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}真是个令人不安的家训
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}不愧是太一先生
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}{\bord3}好了，没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}{\bord3}你可以，你没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}{\bord3}亚季子小姐，还有沙季
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.22,0:08:51.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}欢迎来到我们家
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\3c&495366\4c&495366}从…从今天开始
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&495366\4c&495366}我们就要一起生活啦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.95,0:09:13.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&4C3835\4c&4C3835}在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.91,0:09:17.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}窗帘和床都准备好了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.75,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}但我不清楚你喜欢什么颜色
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}但我不清楚你喜欢什么颜色
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.54,0:09:21.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}要是不喜欢就换掉吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.96,0:09:25.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}桌子我暂时放在窗边了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.17,0:09:27.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}要是想挪位置就跟我说
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.09,0:09:29.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36364C\4c&36364C}{\bord3.5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36364C\4c&36364C}{\bord3.5}好宽敞
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36364C\4c&36364C}{\bord3.5}我觉得挺普通的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36364C\4c&36364C}{\bord3.5}我以前住在破公寓里
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.68,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36364C\4c&36364C}{\bord3.5}是个六叠的单间
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36364C\4c&36364C}{\bord3.5}我甚至没有自己的房间
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.77,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36364C\4c&36364C}{\bord3.5}那你们岂不是要睡在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&38304C\4c&38304C}那你们岂不是要睡在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&38304C\4c&38304C}是…是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&38304C\4c&38304C}不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.53,0:09:50.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&38304C\4c&38304C}妈妈总是值夜班
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.53,0:09:52.74,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&38304C\4c&38304C}生物钟完全颠倒
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&38304C\4c&38304C}所以我一个人睡
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.58,0:09:59.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&38304C\4c&38304C}不过那样的生活应该很自在吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.12,0:10:03.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&38304C\4c&38304C}现在却要和两个男人住在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&38304C\4c&38304C}这倒是没关系
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.25,Dial-CHI,,0,855,0,,{\3c&543D29\4c&543D29}我能问个问题吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.76,0:10:10.92,Dial-CHI,,0,855,0,,{\3c&543D29\4c&543D29}什么问题
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.51,0:10:12.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}就是
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.47,0:10:14.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}你为什么要讲敬语
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.35,0:10:19.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}我不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2E2D38\4c&2E2D38}我们年龄相仿
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2E2D38\4c&2E2D38}你讲话可以随意一些
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2E2D38\4c&2E2D38}年龄相仿算是理由吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.36,0:10:29.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2E2D38\4c&2E2D38}你想啊，同学或者朋友之间
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2E2D38\4c&2E2D38}只讲敬语不是很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}{\bord2}你这是强者的理论吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.74,0:10:36.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}{\bord2}是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.62,0:10:40.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}{\bord2}我无意对你的讲话风格说三道四
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.25,0:10:44.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}{\bord2}如果你是在顾及我的感受
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}{\bord2}我觉得大可不必
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}{\bord2}倒不是在顾及你的感受
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.51,0:10:56.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2C434C\4c&2C434C}我觉得有必要仔细确认一下
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.47,0:10:57.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2C434C\4c&2C434C}就再问你一次
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2C434C\4c&2C434C}也就是说
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2C434C\4c&2C434C}你不希望我讲敬语吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.31,0:11:08.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2C434C\4c&2C434C}是啊，挑明了说
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.19,0:11:10.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2C434C\4c&2C434C}我更喜欢随意的口气
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.57,0:11:15.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}毕竟我不是什么值得尊敬的人
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.74,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}OK
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&483B4C\4c&483B4C}那我就不讲敬语了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&483B4C\4c&483B4C}真干脆啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.04,0:11:27.08,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&483B4C\4c&483B4C}虽然达不到和老朋友对话的程度
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.58,0:11:30.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&483B4C\4c&483B4C}但总不能辜负你这一番推心置腹
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}我也能轻松一些
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&464B4C\4c&464B4C}是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&4F4980\4c&4F4980}果然如我所料
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.01,0:11:44.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}{\3c&414A4C\4c&414A4C}能这样相互磨合，就谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}{\3c&414A4C\4c&414A4C}磨合吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}{\3c&414A4C\4c&414A4C}你说得很对
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.11,0:11:53.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&13294C\4c&13294C}我想和学校的朋友这样相处
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.28,0:11:56.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&13294C\4c&13294C}他们却嘲笑说，这是签合约吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.66,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&13294C\4c&13294C}根本不会认真对待
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那确实挺让人心累的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,所以除了某个人，我和别人都绝交了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你可真极端
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,绝交的都是些无关紧要的人
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&252C38\4c&252C38}我不知道他们的想法
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&252C38\4c&252C38}但他们自己都不愿意把想法说出来
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&2D2F4C\4c&2D2F4C}{\bord2.5}但他们自己都不愿意把想法说出来
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&2D2F4C\4c&2D2F4C}{\bord2.5}我又何必自讨没趣
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\3c&5D5780\4c&5D5780}我来帮你整理行李吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.53,0:12:35.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}你真体贴
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.12,0:14:05.74,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}咦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1C3238\4c&1C3238}绫濑，难道你也在水星高中?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1C3238\4c&1C3238}没错
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.79,0:14:15.08,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1C3238\4c&1C3238}不良少女上重点高中，很吃惊吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.21,0:14:16.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1C3238\4c&1C3238}不
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1C3238\4c&1C3238}我也在那所学校
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你不需要为此道歉
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.68,0:14:28.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}可是…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.93,0:14:31.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&577680\4c&577680}我在学校会尽量装作不认识你
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.27,0:14:36.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&577680\4c&577680}没事，我不在意这个
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.15,0:14:39.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&385280\4c&385280}不过
