Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.95,0:14:46.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\bord3}什么意思
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.25,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2E5866\4c&2E5866}抱歉，我要…
