Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2E5866\4c&2E5866}谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.67,0:15:02.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}是的
