Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}今天吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.23,0:15:16.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&4C3F42\4c&4C3F42}{\bord3}我说后辈
