Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}真的能闻到吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.12,0:15:28.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}香气扑鼻
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}要亲热到什么程度
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.75,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}才能让你满身芬芳呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.75,0:15:34.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我早退了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.75,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0A182B\4c&0A182B}别走，我骗你的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0A182B\4c&0A182B}别丢下我不管
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&221F40\4c&221F40}我只是开玩笑罢了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.55,0:15:45.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&221F40\4c&221F40}你以前提到过你的妹妹
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.26,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}也该见到她了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.60,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}怎么样，可爱吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.52,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}我觉得是个美女
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}和美女同居吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}你的春天来了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}什么都不会发生哦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.32,0:16:03.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}说不定会发生什么哦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.36,0:16:06.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}突然大叔化讲黄段子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}您最好改掉这习惯
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.87,0:16:12.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}从初中到大学全是女校，我也很无奈啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}女校被您贬得一无是处
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.96,0:16:22.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\3c&2E374C\4c&2E374C}说实话，现在不是动歪心思的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&423F4C\4c&423F4C}我在烦恼
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.55,0:16:29.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&423F4C\4c&423F4C}不知道该怎样作为兄长和她相处
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.06,0:16:35.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&335566\4c&335566}我觉得后辈你顺其自然就行了
