Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}瞧你一脸严肃的样子
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&36464C\4c&36464C}没事的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&36464C\4c&36464C}我并没有受到什么虐待
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.10,0:18:44.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}妈妈总是在我上学的时候回家
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}睡觉并做好家务
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}我还没回家她就去上班了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.78,0:18:53.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}这就是我们的日常
