Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.35,0:19:19.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你还没洗澡吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}嗯
