Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}今までどおりとはいかないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}妹ができるんだし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.09,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}妹?
